attr.title: The Best Motorcycle Roads - Vermont Route 17, The Appalachian Gap and Smugglers Notch Pass VT 108
attr.description: A new series featuring some of the best motorcycle roads. This video includes Vermont Route 17, the Appalachian Gap and the Smugglers' Notch Pass on VT 108. More roads to be documented. Video taken using a GoPro HD HERO camera on helmet and suction cup mounts on a Kawasaki ZX-9R. Music: The Stone Roses Fool's Gold and Cypress Hill Rap Superstar instrumental. Videos and more at http://www.worldtrip.ca
